					      <div id="page-title-wrapper" class="js-text-shrink" data-collection-id="546caea8e4b0c4f6bad00c63" data-edit-main-image="Page Banner">
				          <h1 id="page-title" class="page-title">The History Bomb</h1>
				      		<div id="page-description" class="page-description"><p><span style="font-size:16px">Because you fell asleep in history class, The History Bomb seeks to rectify that by telling you all about the fun, awesome, cool, or just downright damn interesting things your teachers missed out on. And then there's the podcast.</span></p></div>
				        </div>
				      

